OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cold with a mix of sunny
OL,6,Fspells and, especially in west,
OL,7,Ffrequent showers which will be heavy
OL,8,Fat times with a risk of hail and
OL,9,Fthunder. Breezy near western coasts
OL,10,Fwith occasionally strong northwesterly
OL,11,Fwinds, winds light in east.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FSome late sunny spells, then
OL,14,Fclear spells overnight, with showers,
OL,15,Fthe showers becoming less frequent but
OL,16,Fstill occasionally heavy. Touch of
OL,17,Ffrost possible in sheltered spots, but
OL,18,Fbreezy near coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,176,160,301,260,100,100
